  {
    "id": "kp-Y8.9-01",
    "section": "Y8.9",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Mean from Frequency Tables",
    "title_zh": "从频数表计算平均数",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "To find the **mean** from a frequency table, you must multiply each value ($x$) by its frequency ($f$) to get $fx$.\n\nThe formula for the mean is: $$\\text{Mean} = \\frac{\\sum fx}{\\sum f}$$\nwhere $\\sum fx$ is the total sum of all data values and $\\sum f$ is the total frequency (total number of items).",
      "zh": "要从频数表中找到**平均数**，必须将每个数值 ($x$) 乘以其对应的频数 ($f$) 以获得 $fx$。\n\n平均数的计算公式为：$$\\text{平均数} = \\frac{\\sum fx}{\\sum f}$$\n其中 $\\sum fx$ 是所有数据值的总和，$\\sum f$ 是总频数（项目总数）。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-mean-table",
        "label": "Calculate mean from discrete data",
        "label_zh": "计算离散数据的平均数",
        "description": "Use a table of scores and frequencies to find the mean score.",
        "description_zh": "利用得分和频数表求平均分。"
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-mode-table",
        "label": "Identify mode from a table",
        "label_zh": "从表中识别众数",
        "description": "Find the value with the highest frequency.",
        "description_zh": "找到频数最高的数值。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-mean-table",
        "question": "The table shows the number of goals scored in 10 matches: \nGoals ($x$): 0, 1, 2, 3 \nFreq ($f$): 2, 4, 3, 1 \nCalculate the mean number of goals.",
        "question_zh": "表显示了 10 场比赛中的进球数：\n进球数 ($x$): 0, 1, 2, 3 \n频数 ($f$): 2, 4, 3, 1 \n计算平均进球数。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Calculate $fx$ values: $0(2)=0, 1(4)=4, 2(3)=6, 3(1)=3$.\n**Step 2:** Find $\\sum fx = 0 + 4 + 6 + 3 = 13$.\n**Step 3:** Find $\\sum f = 2 + 4 + 3 + 1 = 10$.\n**Step 4:** Mean $= 13 \\div 10 = 1.3$.\n**Answer:** $1.3$ goals",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 计算 $fx$ 值：$0(2)=0, 1(4)=4, 2(3)=6, 3(1)=3$。\n**步骤2：** 求 $\\sum fx = 0 + 4 + 6 + 3 = 13$。\n**步骤3：** 求 $\\sum f = 2 + 4 + 3 + 1 = 10$。\n**步骤4：** 平均数 $= 13 \\div 10 = 1.3$。\n**答案：** $1.3$ 个进球",
        "source": "Year 8 Assessment"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-mode-table",
        "question": "Using the table from the previous example, identify the modal number of goals.",
        "question_zh": "使用上一个例子中的表，识别进球数的众数。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Look for the highest frequency. The highest frequency is $4$.\n**Step 2:** Identify the goal number corresponding to frequency $4$. It is $1$.\n**Answer:** $1$ goal",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 寻找最高频数。最高频数是 $4$。\n**步骤2：** 识别频数 $4$ 对应的进球数，是 $1$。\n**答案：** $1$ 个进球",
        "source": "Adapted from Y8 curriculum"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
